@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nGET /api/invoices" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Invoice" as DB
User->UI: Open the invoice page
UI->API: Request invoice list
API->DB: Retrieve invoice records
DB-->API: Return invoice data
API-->UI: Return invoice list
UI-->User: Display invoice details

@enduml
